1105
01:00:33,570 --> 01:00:35,479
Uh! Uh!

1106
01:00:38,810 --> 01:00:40,514
Làm tốt lắm, Kid!

1107
01:00:41,090 --> 01:00:44,273
Xem ai đến này.
Xem ai đến này. Wow.

1108
01:00:44,330 --> 01:00:46,194
